%F A027434 G.f.: x*(1 + x^(-1/4)*theta_2(x) + theta_3(x))/(2*(1 - x)), where theta_k(x) is the Jacobi theta function. - _Ilya Gutkovskiy_, Jul 20 2016
%F A027434 a(n) = 1 + floor(sqrt(4*n-1)). - _Chai Wah Wu_, Jul 27 2022
